# Catalog/Export Sync Rule

- If `config/comprehensive_data_element_list.json` is updated, verify whether export artifacts or export-generating logic must also be updated in the same change.
- At minimum, check for impacts to `src/export_llm_context_snapshot.py` and any generated export outputs that depend on catalog fields.
- Do not treat catalog-only changes as complete when downstream exports are stale or inconsistent.
